public class vxi11core_DEVICE_ASYNC_Client
extends org.acplt.oncrpc.OncRpcClientStub

The class vxi11core_DEVICE_ASYNC_Client implements the client stub proxy for the DEVICE_ASYNC remote program. It provides method stubs which, when called, in turn call the appropriate remote method (procedure).
